\f0 \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 The meanings of their names - His means God\'92s grace yet he leverage God\'92s grace for his personal gain. \'a0We do that all the time. \'a0We forget that God is graceful but He is also holy. \'a0Much like you love your kids more than anything but that doesn\'92t mean they can do whatever they want. \'a0 Her name meant beautiful\'85she may have been on the outside but her heart was ugly. \'a0Both were hypocrites pretending to be one thing on the outside while on the inside they were something else.
\f1 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls7\ilvl1
\f0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 It would be easy to see them as generous but that wasn\'92t the case. \'a0If money is your god then yes, they were generous but money wasn\'92t their god\'85it was accolades. \'a0They wanted personal praise and they were willing to sacrifice financial means to get what they really wanted\'85what they were really craving in life. \'a0They weren\'92t generous. \'a0This was a business transaction.
\f1 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls7\ilvl1
\f0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
